engine-feedback/INDEX.md:33:**Note on direct-to-inbox placement**: records above (EF-051 / EF-053 / EF-054 / EF-055 / EF-058×3 plus the EF-047×3 set from S047 arc-plan design work) originated in self-dev out-of-session discussion or substrate exercise, not from external-application execution. Operator directed direct placement in `inbox/` rather than fabricating provenance by routing through an external workspace's `outbox/` (which would contaminate that workspace's execution record). `source_workspace_id` accurately reflects self-dev origin. The `engine-feedback/` schema per `workspace-structure.md` v7 §engine-feedback describes the external-workspace→self-dev-inbox direction but does not forbid self-dev-originating records being placed directly in inbox; the practical discipline is accurate attribution via `source_workspace_id` and `reported_by` fields. **Operator-surfaced post-session intakes** (EF-054 first-of-record at S053-post-session; EF-055 second-of-record at S055-post-session; EF-058×3 third-through-fifth-of-record at S058-post-session) are a recognised sub-pattern within direct-to-inbox; all carry `reported_by: operator` (vs. `application-agent` for substrate-exercise-originated records EF-051 / EF-053). **EF-058×3 is the first-of-record post-session-intake-triple event**: three related records filed in one post-session discussion sequencing as (a) operational defect-fix path → (b) methodological observation about MAD shared-context discipline → (c) meta-pattern observation about Tier 2 validation discipline that subsumes (a)+(b); the triple establishes a discussion-pattern in which a single operator-surfaced gap surfaces operational + methodological + structural layers in sequence as the discussion deepens. **EF-058×3 triage at S059** (D-207 + D-208 + D-209): all three records triaged in one session; one resolved (uv-migration as defect-fix Path T+L) + two substantive-arc-deferred (claude-md-drift + tier-2-validation per intake dispositions); bundled-Path-T+L pattern reified at n=2 (S054 EF-053+EF-054 first-instance multi-intake same-session resolution; S059 EF-058×3 second-instance with mix of same-session-resolution + deferred-to-future-MAD).
