    11	# Workspace Structure
    12	
    13	## Purpose
    14	
    15	This specification defines how the workspace is organized: what directories and files exist, what each contains, and how they relate. It ensures that any agent or person reading the workspace can orient themselves quickly and knows where to find — and where to put — each kind of content.
