   311	
   312	New top-level directories may be created by future sessions when the work demands them (e.g., `implementations/`, `examples/`). Any new directory should be documented by updating this specification. `applications/` was defined by Session 009 (D-054) for external artefacts and is no longer a hypothetical example. `engine-feedback/` was defined by Session 036 (D-116) for external-application engine/methodology feedback intake.
